item.title: 【Live Audios (lossless)】FLAC - Paramore - 2010/10/08 - Auckland, New Zealand (Audience recording)
item.description:
I saw this one on Archive.org and my download speed was so slow i uploaded it on Mega.

Paramore
2010-10-08 Auckland, New Zealand
2010
657kbps

Vector Arena

Source: Sony ECM-717 > IRiverH320

Location: Centre By Soundboard

Notes from the original poster:

I don't know much Paramore (I know, betraying my heritage), but this is a good tape from an Antipodean leg of the Brand New Eyes tour. 10 of the album's 11 songs feature, plus the show ending in a triumphant 'Misery Business' before they decided to abandon it.

Track listing:
[intro]
Ignorance
Feeling Sorry
That's What You Get
For a Pessimist, I'm Pretty Optimistic
Emergency
Playing God
Careful
Decode
You Ain't Woman Enough (To Take My Man) [Loretta Lynn cover]
When It Rains [acoustic]
Where the Lines Overlap [acoustic]
Misguided Ghosts [acoustic]
Crushcrushcrush
Pressure
Looking Up
The Only Exception
Brick by Boring Brick
Misery Business

2, 3, 7, 8, 9, 12, 13, 16, 17, and 18 from Brand New Eyes; 4, 5, 11, 14, and 19 from Riot; 6 and 15 from All We Know Is Falling.

Use Base64 to decode and see the Mega link

item.title: 【HD Live Performances】HDTV - Katy Perry - California Gurls (MuchMusic Video Awards, Canada, 2010)
item.description:
I included 2 files: one is the original which looks like a mess (interlacing, blocking artifacts because too low bitrate for interlacing, noise) and another one is my attempt to fix it (deinterlace with QTGMC, deblocking, denoising, resizing down to remove more blocking and noise). The audio is identical for both files. Pick whatever version you prefer (or both).
